         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne botanic Garden, ¶ 11/3/72. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ In compliance with your instructions I have the honor of submitting to you an estimate of the expenditure, which I would recommend for the service of th...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">72.03.11</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Charles<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Gavan<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Duffy</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">G72/7643, unit 750, VPRS 44 inwards registered and unregistered correspondence, VA 538 Department of Crown Lands and Survey, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter registered in the Chief Secretary's Department in March 1872 (A72/2606) and transferred to the Lands Department on 22 April. See W. Odgers to M, 25 April 1872.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to J. Grant,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>9 April 1872,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is a copy of this letter incorporating some changes. Grant was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>again President of the Board of Land and Works, the Minister responsible for the Botanic Garden.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                  </p>
               </note>Melbourne botanic Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">11/3/72.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In compliance with your instructions I have the honor of submitting to you an estimate of the expenditure, which I would recommend for the service of the botanic Garden during the financial year from 1 July 1872 till 30 June 1873.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Government's Botanist and Director</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£610</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Clerk<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                                    <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>and Accountant<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">deleted</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                              </p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(with quarters)</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£160</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Head Gardener (with quarters)<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M added a marginal note at this point: 'This item is provided for a foreman, as the Forest Inspector [i.e. William Ferguson] is likely to be engaged in his Forest duties continually hereafter. In order that an educated gentleman, such as the Clerk, may not be placed under a Gardener, I have this time provided for him specially, whereas formerly he was paid out of the general vote.'</p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£150</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Wages of Gardeners, one Laboratory Attendant, one Museum Operator, one Signwriter, one Artisan, one bot. Collector, one Carter, one Engine Driver, one Messenger, and several labourers</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£2370</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Expense of publishing works on Austral. plants £100 and purchase of Museum materials, plants and seeds</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£130<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>£130<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">above</seg>
                                 <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>£230<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>deleted.</seg>
                              </p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Stores, Timber, Stationery, Flowerpots, Bricks, Water pipes, Drainpipes, Paint, Tools, Glass &amp;c Coals for engine &amp;c</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£220</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Forage for one carthorse and food for birds and other animals</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£80</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Incidental, Transit and Travelling Expenses</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£140</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Reward to Orphanboys to be placed into the Savings Bank (35/ a week)</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£91</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Cartage of Streetmanure</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£40</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Test plantation in the Ranges</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£120</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Books and Instruments</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£80</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">Total</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border-top: 0.0104in solid #000000; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; border-right: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£4091<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                                    <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The amounts listed total<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>£4191.</p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Remarks</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Directors Position is heavily taxed by many expenses in relation to foreign interchanges, scientific communications abroad, calls of visitors, for which the votes make no provision. The Director lives merely in an office ever since 1857, not even a single private room being provided. A small item is now provided for books and instruments, even that expenditure having fallen largely on his private means formerly, so office light, personal travelling expenses, much of outlay for conveyance to proceed to town offices. The Director has no allowance for a servant, nor for a horse, nor forage &amp;c.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In accordance with a recent recommendation of the Director special provision has been made for the salary of a headgardener, but in order that the latter may not be placed over the Clerk and Accountant, who was formerly paid out of the general Wages vote, it is recommended that the Clerks Salary should in future like that of a headgardner appear separately on the estimates. These two items are saved out of the wages vote. No vacancy or position for a Clerk and Accountant is created, as the Gentleman, who holds this position since several years,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Georg Luehmann.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has discharged his functions to my full satisfaction.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The item for publishing of plants includes a grant to the President of the Linnéan Society<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn6" n="7">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>George Bentham.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for 30 copies of the work published by him and Baron von Mueller in England.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn7" n="8">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham (1863-78).</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The item for incidental expenses includes outlays for small repairs.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The new item of gratuity to the boys of the industr. Schools is to reward them in succession and rotation for good conduct, and particularly for securing the safe going to and from the barracks, without further loss of time of the gardeners to watch over the arrival and departure of the various sets of boys over the extensive ground.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The obtaining of street scrapings for manuring through the only cart and horse of the Department is an impossibility; hence the small new item.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As a trial for teagrowth and other industrial cultures in the first instance at Fernshaw<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn8" n="9">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the sum for one test plantation is provided. It is kept as small as ever possible.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir, your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gov. Botanist and Director of the botanic Garden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">No provision is made for the Inspector of forests on my estimates, as I understand that the services of this Officer are to be devoted entirely to Forest Work under the Lands Department.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
